{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9a1369a87b","title":"湖南省长沙市中级人民法院关于朱正的刑事判决书","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6f405efd4a","index":0,"year":1979,"month":1,"day":21,"articleId":"9a1369a87b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dce00e6de9","name":"湖南文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4516dc3877","type":"title","text":"湖南省长沙市中级人民法院关于朱正的刑事判决书","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9a1369a87b"},{"id":"865f9d0a97","type":"paragraph","text":"朱正，曾用名企生、郑珠、夏怀，男，现年四十七岁，长沙市人，住本市朝阳新村八十八号。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9a1369a87b"},{"id":"3d01f23a8e","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七一年四月二十七日，长沙市革委会人保部、市公安机关军管会以(71)军公刑字第120号刑事判决书，以现行反革命犯罪判处朱正有期徒刑三年，强制劳动改造。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9a1369a87b"},{"id":"7db944f56c","type":"paragraph","text":"经本院再审查明：朱正在文化大革命中的一些言论主要是议论“四人帮”的，原以反革命犯罪判刑是错误的。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9a1369a87b"},{"id":"d1f09078f5","type":"paragraph","text":"据此，本院依法判决如下：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9a1369a87b"},{"id":"25742891fc","type":"paragraph","text":"撤销一九七一年四月二十七日市革委会人保部、市公安机关军管会(71)军公刑字第120号刑事判决书，对朱正宣告无罪。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9a1369a87b"},{"id":"a547a6808d","type":"paragraph","text":" 一九七九年二月十五日","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9a1369a87b"},{"id":"0346144f20","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：朱正《小书生大时代》，北京大学出版社，1999年。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9a1369a87b"}],"page":{"id":"069c7a5ee7","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9a1369a87b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}